ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: It's a difficult class but the professor makes it easier to understand. I would recommend it to some students who are interested in any kind of modeling.
I would recommend it to my fellows in their first year as good preparation for math skills.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: I'm interested in using mathematical modeling to approach some components of my dissertation so this course has been very helpful.
It provides some interesting numerical models and algorithms that may be helpful for my research.
